divs: Sighting DetailsI was only 8 years old and it was about mid day i have never told anyone so i hope no one knows besides you because i dont want people to think im nuts but 12 years later i still remember it plain as day. my dad one of his friends i cant remember who was with and i were driving somewhere its so long ago... sorry i remember see it was like different colored lights and they kept going it was mid day and it was so weird to see lights on at that time but it so just above the corn... i remember exactly how the went blue to green to red to yellow to orange i never said anything because i was to scared of what my family would think. i was scared but fascinated at the same time i was just wondering what i saw.
